    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready to get the job done? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and is perfect for someone who values reliability over a showroom finish! It shows some genuine character from its years on the road, but it remains a solid performer that\u2019s ready for many more miles. If you're looking for a practical, budget-friendly option that you can count on, this is the one for you!",
